data.title: Is there a reason why there are so many artists with the name "Art"?
data.meta_description: Answer: Oh here we go…I am an artist, my name is Arthur…My dad was a POW in world war II..He named me after general Douglas MacArthur…In elementary school I acquired the nickname “Mac”.. Thank God I am still addressed like that…I became a artist…Like I said “ oh here we go “…like..Art by Arthur…....
